ls-help-change-roles-employers-hiring-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20for%20AI-related%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20surged%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20pool%20of%20potential%20workers%20with%20the%20educational%20background%20and%20technical%20know-how%20to%20train%20large%20language%20models%2C%20write%20AI%20algorithms%2C%20and%20engineer%20new%20AI%20applications%20hasn't%20kept%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErik%20Garcell%2C%20director%20of%20quantum%20enterprise%20development%20at%20quantum%20computing%20software%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fclassiq-powers-quantum-breakthrough-with-sumitomo-corporation-and-mizuho-dl-financial-technology-1034510728%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClassiq%20Technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20quantum%20computing%20companies%20have%20taken%20notice%20of%20the%20hiring%20challenges%20facing%20the%20AI%20industry%20and%20are%20trying%20to%20circumvent%20them%20before%20they%20become%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Classiq%2C%20we%20actually%20have%20a%20whole%20academic%20program%20we're%20kicking%20off%20here%2C%20working%20with%20universities%20to%20deploy%20quantum%20curriculum%2C%20because%20not%20every%20school%20has%20one%2C%20and%20those%20that%20do%2C%20we're%20trying%20to%20advocate%20for%20more%20of%20the%20hands-on%20practicum%20side%20of%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20published%20by%20the%20international%20consulting%20firm%20Randstad%20in%20November%20found%20that%2075%25%20of%20companies%20adopt%20AI%20and%20hire%20for%20AI-related%20roles.%20Still%2C%20just%2035%25%20of%20talent%20have%20received%20AI%20training%20in%20the%20last%20year.%20That%20labor%20pool%20comes%20with%20a%20significant%20age%20gap%2C%20with%20just%20one%20in%20five%20baby%20boomers%20being%20offered%20AI%20skill%20development%20opportunities%2C%20compared%20to%20almost%20half%20of%20Gen%20Z%20workers%2C%20and%20a%2042%20percentage%20point%20gender%20gap%20favoring%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20gap%20persists%20despite%20a%20surge%20in%20the%20need%20for%20new%20talent.%20PwC%20found%20in%20its%202024%20Job%20Barometer%20that%20the%20share%20of%20jobs%20that%20require%20specialized%20AI%20skills%20has%20grown%20700%25%20since%202016%20%E2%80%94%20three%20times%20the%20rate%20of%20other%20job%20types%20%E2%80%94%20and%20having%20AI%20skills%20comes%20with%20the%20potential%20for%20a%2025%25%20wage%20premium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20talent%20pool%20in%20the%20quantum%20industry%2C%20which%20is%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20size%20of%20the%20AI%20field%2C%20is%20even%20smaller%2C%20but%20demand%20is%20growing.%20The%20trade%20publication%20The%20Quantum%20Insider%20reported%20that%20quantum%20computing%20is%20expected%20to%20create%20an%20estimated%20250%2C000%20new%20jobs%20by%202030%2C%20jumping%20to%20840%2C000%20by%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224882bb21-6649-4806-9a50-67301bc166f4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreparing%20for%20quantum's%20'ChatGPT%20moment'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQuantum%20computing%20is%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20field%20attracting%20major%20interest%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-race-big-tech-microsoft-google-amazon-ibm-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20giants%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20IBM%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Google.%20Since%20it%20combines%20computer%20science%2C%20math%2C%20and%20quantum%20mechanics%2C%20it%20remains%20deeply%20technical%20and%20expensive%20to%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20industry%20is%20still%20in%20its%20infancy%2C%20Garcell%20said%20the%20major%20players%20in%20the%20quantum%20field%20believe%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquantum-computing-could-improve-medicine-climate-logistics-world-hunger-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epotential%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20advancements%20in%20medicine%2C%20materials%20science%2C%20and%20cybersecurity%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0are%20worth%20early%20investment%20to%20ensure%20a%20talent%20shortage%20doesn't%20derail%20its%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIBM%20really%20did%20put%20out%20quite%20a%20lot%20of%20really%20good%20educational%20content%20for%20quantum%20computing%3B%20they%20nurtured%20the%20industry%20very%20early%20on%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcell%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20happy%20to%20say%20that%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20really%20great%20learning%20available%2C%20same%20with%20companies%20like%20Pennylane%2C%20just%20great%20educational%20content%20for%20free%20that%20you%20can%20start%20diving%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIBM%20has%20partnered%20with%20quantum%20startups%20like%20Q-CTRL%20to%20build%20its%20quantum%20learning%20program%2C%20which%20includes%20free%20online%20courses%20outlining%20fundamental%20topics%20like%20building%20quantum%20algorithms%20and%20error-correcting%20codes.%20Other%20companies%2C%20like%20Google%2C%20Pennylane%2C%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20offer%20similar%20independent%20courses%20with%20certificates%20of%20completion%20to%20identify%20those%20with%20in-demand%20quantum%20skills%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdirector-sap-labs-explains-qualifications-culture-quantum-computing-field-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecruiters%20are%20searching%20for%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20the%20University%20of%20Chicago%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20offer%20some%20of%20the%20most%20comprehensive%20quantum%20computing%20courses%20available%20at%20academic%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarcell%20said%20he%20recently%20taught%20a%20three-day%20introductory%20course%20at%20MIT%20to%20introduce%20the%20university's%20student%20body%20to%20qua