ider.com%2Fmost-beautiful-place-every-continent-according-to-frequent-traveler-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etraveled%20across%20six%20continents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20held%20dream%20jobs%2C%20and%20met%20celebrities%2C%20politicians%2C%20and%20royalty.%20I%20own%20my%20own%20house%2C%20where%20I%20proudly%20display%20a%20black-and-white%20photo%20of%20my%20maternal%20family%2C%20a%20reminder%20of%20who%20I%20have%20to%20thank%20for%20everything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20have%20an%20overwhelming%20secret%3A%20I%20am%20tired%20deep%20in%20my%20bones%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20hustle%20anymore.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bef556e0-2acf-4301-a243-20ab25964423%5C%22%3EI'd%20love%20the%20simple%20life%20my%20ancestors%20had%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20I%20yearn%20for%20the%20Neapolitan%20castle%20towns%20and%20Irish%20fields%20my%20ancestors%20had.%20I%20flip%20through%20Instagram%20cheap%20home%20accounts%2C%20dreaming%20of%20fixer-uppers%20in%20Abruzzo%2C%20of%20eating%20fragrant%20tomatoes%20off%20the%20vine%2C%20and%20gossiping%20with%20neighbors%20in%20communal%20gardens.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'd%20love%20a%20simple%20life.%20I'd%20love%20to%20find%20a%20slower%20treadmill.%20I%20crave%20time%20to%20absorb%20art%20and%20literature%2C%20see%20beauty%20with%20my%20own%20eyes%2C%20and%20meet%20new%20people.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20name%20every%20star%20in%20the%20sky.%20But%20if%20I%20stop%20climbing%20and%20achieving%20accolades%2C%20am%20I%20letting%20them%20down%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20lots%20of%20science%20behind%20the%20psychology%20of%20big%20expectations.%20It's%20very%20common%20to%20feel%20the%20bruising%20weight%20of%20family%20traditions%20picking%20our%20paths%20in%20life.%20And%20when%20those%20relatives%20are%20deceased%2C%20there's%20the%20added%20emotion%20of%20wondering%20if%20you've%20done%20everything%20you%20could%20with%20the%20time%20you%20have%20been%20given.%20We%20all%20want%20the%20people%20we%20love%20to%20be%20proud%20of%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%202007%20analysis%20of%20research%20by%20scientists%20Todd%20Rogers%20and%20Katy%20Milkman%20brings%20this%20emotion%20into%20perspective%20with%20an%20everyday%20choice.%20Think%20about%20the%20mundane%20task%20of%20walking%20through%20the%20grocery%20store.%20You%20may%20aim%20to%20eat%20healthier%2C%20but%20you%20pass%20right%20by%20the%20apples%20and%20instead%20decide%20to%20treat%20yourself%20with%20a%20chocolate%20bar.%20Rogers%20and%20Milkman%20call%20that%20moment%20of%20consideration%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.library.hbs.edu%2Fworking-knowledge%2Funderstanding-the-want-vs-should-decision%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20should-self%20vs.%20the%20want-self%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20what%20should%20I%20do%20versus%20what%20do%20I%20actually%20want%20to%20do%2C%20and%20you%20can%20find%20this%20psychological%20phenomenon%20far%20beyond%20the%20supermarket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20chocolate%20bar%20example%2C%20instant%20gratification%20is%20the%20basic%20premise%20behind%20the%20want-self.%20What%20will%20make%20you%20happy%20right%20now%3F%20That%20feeling%20battles%20the%20should-self%2C%20which%20aims%20for%20choices%20we%20believe%20will%20have%20a%20greater%20future%20outcome.%20The%20should-self%20creates%20a%20mental%20list%20of%20long-term%20benefits%20that%20will%20provide%20for%20a%20better%20future.%20In%20Psychology%20Today%2C%20psychotherapist%20and%20author%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psychologytoday.com%2Fus%2Fblog%2Finviting-monkey-tea%2F202208%2Fshould-vs-want-freeing-yourself-the-shoulding-habit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENancy%20Colier%20takes%20this%20a%20step%20further%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20drawing%20a%20correlation%20between%20wanting%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20conscientious%2C%20good%20person%20who%20is%20motivated%20to%20create%20a%20better%20future%20or%20being%20seen%20as%20someone%20who%20takes%20what%20they%20want%20now.%20The%20problem%20here%20is%20that%20a%20list%20of%20%26quot%3Bshoulds%26quot%3B%20can%20be%20subjective.%20These%20%26quot%3Bshoulds%26quot%3B%20could%20come%20from%20a%20cultural%20standard%2C%20like%20thinking%20we%20need%20a%20specific%20title%20at%20work%20or%20thinking%20we%20need%20to%20look%20one%20way%20when%20our%20body%20is%20built%20another%20way.%20It%20can%20even%20come%20from%20family%20traditions%20that%20are%20long%20outdated%20from%20being%20beneficial%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209219b63-ba22-4161-8da1-cd29365af84a%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20focusing%20on%20what%20I%20want%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20moments%20of%20my%20happy%2C%20privileged%20life%20beg%20the%20question%2C%20%26quot%3BAm%20I%20doing%20enough%3F%26quot%3B%20Am%20I%20maximizing%20every%20opportunity%20presented%20to%20me%3F%20Have%20I%20scaled%20to%20the%20highest%20rung%20of%20the%20career%20ladder%20and%20become%20perfect%20in%20my%20social%20life%3F%20What%20do%20my%20ancestors%20think%20about%20what%20I've%20done%20with%20the%20freedom%20allotted%20to%20me%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20recently%2C%20and%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20reading%20and%20research%2C%20I'm%20flipping%20this%20story%20on%20its%20head.%20No%20more%20%26quot%3Bshoulds%26quot%3B%20that%20make%20me%20tired%20and%20sick%3B%20I'm%20inviting%20in%20more%20%26quot%3Bwants.%26quot%3B%20Isn't%20part%20of%20having%20a%20choice%20accepting%20what%20I%20really%20want%20to%20do%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBeing%20my%20best%20self%20is%20not%20strictly%20adhering%20to%20what%20I%20believe%20I%20should%20do%20to%20make%20others%20happy%20but%20understanding%20how%20to%20be%20happiest%20in%20the%20time%20allotted%20to%20me.%20And%20hopefully%2C%20that%20is%20exactly%20what%20would%20make%20the%20Anna's%20and%20Maria's%20proud%2C%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdealing-with-expectations-of-succcess-in-family-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745698681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f6df263fe8d3928362a39c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdealing-with-expectations-of-succcess-in-family-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20questioned%20whether%20I'm%20doing%20enough%20with%20my%20life.%20But%20now%20I'm%20focusing%20more%20on%20my%20wants%20rather%20than%20on%20what%20I%20feel%20I%20should%20be%20doing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Annemarie%20Dooling)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdealing-with-expectations-of-succcess-in-family-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Escort%20Boys%E2%80%99%20Producer%20on%20Taking%20the%20Raunchy%20French%20Comedy%20to%20%E2%80%98Darker%E2%80%99%20Ground%20in%20Season%202%20and%20Developing%20Projects%20with%20Amanda%20Sthers%2C%20Olivier%20Abbou%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745695952000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FEscort-Boys-s02-l-Thibaut-Evrard-Simon-Ehrlacher-Guillaume-Labbe-Corentin-Fila-l-Eloise-Legay.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236378661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20tackling%20gender%20power%20dynamics%20in%20the%20post%20%23MeToo%20era%2C%20Prime%20Video%E2%80%99s%20raunchy%20comedy%20series%20%E2%80%9CEscort%20Boys%E2%80%9D%20is%20returning%20for%20a%20second%20season%20that%E2%80%99s%20several%20shades%20darker%20and%20is%