%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680a694da466d2b74ab41076%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20latex%20layers%20come%20in%20soft%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20firm%2C%20while%20the%20coils%20are%20plush%20or%20firm.%20They%20combine%20to%20offer%20five%20comfort%20options%20on%20each%20side%20of%20the%20bed.%3Cp%3ENaturepedic%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20is%20made%20of%20organic%20materials%20and%20sports%20an%20array%20of%20eco-friendly%20certifications%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ul.com%2Fservices%2Ful-greenguard-certification%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGreenguard%20Gold%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmadesafe.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMade%20Safe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal-standard.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOTS%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ewg.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnvironmental%20Working%20Group%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mattress%20features%20a%20quilted%20top%20layer%20that%20zips%20off%2C%20though%20it's%20spot-clean%20only.%20It's%20made%20of%20organic%20cotton%2C%20fire-retardant%20wool%20batting%2C%20and%20PLA%2C%20a%20fiber%20made%20from%20non-GMO%20sugarcane%20that%20adds%20improved%20moisture%20wicking%20and%20durability.%20Below%20that%20is%20a%203-inch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.controlunion.com%2Fcertification-program%2Fgols-global-organic-latex-standard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGOLS-certified%3C%2Fa%3E%20organic%20latex%20layer%2C%20which%20responds%20to%20your%20body's%20contours%20to%20provide%20pressure-point%20relief.%20Next%20is%20an%208-inch%20layer%20of%20encased%20coils%20with%20added%20edge%20support.%20The%20base%20is%20organic%20cotton%20batting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defining%20feature%20of%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20is%20that%20you%20can%20choose%20how%20firm%20you%20want%20each%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20to%20be%3A%20Plush%2C%20Medium%2C%20Cushion-Firm%2C%20Firm%2C%20and%20Extra-Firm.%20The%20firmness%20of%20the%20coils%20and%20latex%20layer%20will%20depend%20on%20your%20choice.%20The%20mattress%20is%20available%20in%20the%20six%20standard%20sizes%2C%20ranging%20from%20twin%20to%20California%20king.%20For%20sizes%20queen%20and%20larger%2C%20you%20can%20pick%20different%20firmnesses%20for%20each%20side%20of%20the%20bed.%20I%20tested%20a%20queen-sized%20Naturepedic%20with%20one%20side%20Plush%20(soft%20latex%2C%20plush%20coils)%20and%20the%20other%20Medium%20(medium%20latex%2C%20plush%20coils)%20to%20best%20suit%20my%20side%20sleeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b73bb491-4d44-4d21-8331-c6db50c95838%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Our%20review%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20review%20of%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20Mattress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d7fcdfe-f35d-4050-b99b-98de0d96a475%5C%22%3ESetup%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221576%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20Organic%20Mattress%20is%20shown%20still%20in%20the%20four%20boxes%20it%20arrives%20in.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680a68fa3fe8d3928363f869%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221182%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20arrives%20in%20four%20boxes.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20customization%20of%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%2C%20the%20assembly%20process%20is%20more%20involved%20than%20that%20of%20most%20beds.%20While%20most%20come%20in%20a%20single%20box%20the%20size%20of%20a%20mini%20fridge%2C%20the%20EOS%20Classic%20arrived%20in%20four%20smaller%20boxes%2C%20which%20made%20it%20a%20lot%20easier%20to%20carry%20up%20to%20my%20third-floor%20testing%20room%20and%20may%20enable%20you%20to%20up%20the%20bed%20without%20extra%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20setup%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20It%20took%20me%20about%2020%20minutes%2C%20and%20by%20the%20time%20I%20was%20done%2C%20I%20was%20dripping%20sweat.%20Naturepedic%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYLLzwL47ADw%26list%3DTLGGDUlAKLxN79AxODA0MjAyNQ%26ab_channel%3DNaturepedic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20helpful%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20explains%20the%20process.%20First%2C%20you%20lay%20the%20mattress%20encasement%20across%20your%20bed%20frame%20and%20unzip%20it%20to%20make%20room%20for%20the%20internal%20components.%20Next%2C%20you%20add%20the%20coils%2C%20squeezing%20them%20into%20the%20encasement.%20Then%2C%20put%20the%20latex%20layers%20on%20top%20of%20those%2C%20ensuring%20your%20preferred%20firmness%20is%20on%20your%20side%20of%20the%20bed.%20Lastly%2C%20you%20zip%20the%20encasement%20closed%20and%20lie%20down%20for%20a%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221576%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20Organic%20Mattress%20is%20displayed%20partially%20assembled%20in%20a%20bedroom.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680a6a4fa466d2b74ab410a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221182%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAssembly%20of%20the%20Naturepedic%20mattress%20is%20more%20involved%20than%20most%20beds%20in%20a%20box.%20I%20was%20sweating%20by%20the%20time%20I%20finished.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20that%20it%20was%20fully%20expanded%20out%20of%20the%20box%20and%20lacked%20the%20initial%20odor%20most%20beds%20have.%20Naturepedic%20offers%20in-home%20setup%20(i.e.%2C%20white-glove%20delivery)%20for%20an%20additional%20charge%20that%20varies%20depending%20on%20location.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.naturepedic.com%2Fcontact-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EContact%20customer%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20rates%20in%20your%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226086f819-d303-4dd3-80ab-d5c2490fe3fe%5C%22%3EComfort%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20month%20I%20slept%20on%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%2C%20I%20enjoyed%20outstanding%20pressure%20relief%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20bed.%20I'm%20on%20the%20heavier%20side%2C%20athletically%20built%3A%206%20feet%20tall%20and%20225%20pounds.%20I%20can%20sleep%20in%20any%20position%2C%20but%20I%20prefer%20sleeping%20on%20my%20side.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20medium%20and%20plush%20latex%20comfort%20layers%20seemed%20to%20be%20perfectly%20suited%20for%20side%20sleepers.%20I%20felt%20my%20spine%20stayed%20aligned%20as%20it%20cradled%20my%20body%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20wake%20up%20sore%20while%20sleeping%20on%20the%20EOS%20Classic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20track%20my%20sleep%20every%20night%20using%20a%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd7b942020d58583e05af28a6618df74dc5a87aca22b7c55c4346212d92adb566%26postID%3D680a5ea818fa53306323dcb0%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fnaturepedic-eos-classic-organic-mattress-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.garmin.com%252Fen-US%252Fp%252F698632%252Fpn%252F010-02383-00%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGarmin%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20all-time%20average%20sleep%20score%20is%2063%20out%20of%20100.%20On%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%2C%20my%20sleep%20was%20better%20than%20average%20at%2065.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20scale%20of%201%20to%2010%2C%20where%2010%20is%20the%20firmest%2C%20I'd%20rate%20the%20Plush%20side%20a%205.%20It%20was%20soft%20but%20maintained%20good%20support%20as%20I%20didn't%20sink%20in%20too%20much.%20The%20Medium%20side%20was%20a%206%2C%20just%20slightly%20firmer.%20While%20the%20Plush%20side%20is%20likely%20only%20good%20for%20petite%20individuals%20and%20side%20sleepers%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Medium%20firmness%20will%20appeal%20to%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20people%2C%20including%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers.%20Heavier%20back%20and%20stomach%20sleepers%20might%20want%20to%20consider%20one%20of%20the%20firmer%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd35e09b-5f7e-4772-aa0b-763c3bc2102a%5C%22%3EHeat%20dissipation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20a%20laser%20thermometer%20to%20measure%20how%20cool%20mattresses%20stay%20and%20how%20quickly%20they%20dissipate%20heat.%20I%20do%20this%20by%20taking%20temperature%20readings%20before%20bed%2C%20when%20I%20get%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20two%20minutes%20after%20getting%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20readings%20showed%20that%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20did%20not%20dissipate%20heat%20well.%20When%20I%20first%20got%20up%20from%20the%20mattress%2C%20it%20was%2089.5%20degrees%20Fahrenheit%2C%20which%20is%20exactly%20the%20average%20across%20all%20my%20mattress%20testing.%20However%2C%20the%20heat%20tended%20to%20stay%20put%2C%20only%20decreasing%20by%20about%20nine%20degrees%20in%20the%20next%20two%20minutes.%20Most%20mattresses%20I've%20tested%20drop%20in%20temperature%20by%2012%20degrees%20or%20more%20in%20those%20two%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20I%20frequently%20overheated%20on%20the%20Naturepedic.%20Consequently%2C%20I%20suggest%20hot%20sleepers%20supplement%20the%20bed%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-cooling-products-for-better-sleep%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecooling%20products%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20look%20elsewhere.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20cold%20sleepers%20may%20find%20it%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22141b41cb-037b-471d-aa41-2792d782ed41%5C%22%3EEdge%20support%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEdge%20support%20is%20an%20important%20feature%20because%20it%20makes%20getting%20into%20and%20out%20of%20bed%20easier%20and%20ensures%20you%20feel%20comfortable%20across%20the%20mattress's%20surface%2C%20even%20on%20the%20periphery.%20I%20assess%20edge%20support%20using%20two%20tests.%20First%2C%20I%20use%20a%20yardstick%20to%20measure%20how%20much%20the%20edge%20sinks%20when%20I%20sit%20on%20the%20side.%20Second%2C%20I%20lie%20on%20the%20very%20edge%20and%20roll%20until%20I%20fall.%20If%20I%20make%20it%20beyond%20a%2045-degree%20angle%20to%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20mattress%20has%20pretty%20good%20edge%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic's%20edge%20support%20is%20great.%20While%20sitting%20on%20it%2C%20the%20edge%20sinkage%20was%20about%20average%2C%20but%20when%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20I%20got%20pretty%20far%20before%20I%20fell%20off.%20Plus%2C%20subjectively%2C%20I%20felt%20quite%20comfortable%20lying%20on%20the%20side.%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20I%20might%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8979cbe-da8f-49d5-9b90-4665e4d86edd%5C%22%3EMotion%20isolation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bed%20with%20good%20motion%20isolation%20will%20keep%20you%20from%20feeling%20your%20partner%20toss%20and%20turn%20in%20the%20night%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20get%20jostled%20awake.%20I%20test%20motion%20isolation%20by%20placing%20a%20vibrometer%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20dropping%20a%2015-pound%20bowling%20ball%20on%20the%20other%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20several%20iterations%20of%20the%20test%2C%20the%20Naturepedic%20mattress%20showed%20impressive%20motion%20isolation.%20The%20average%20in%20my%20mattress%20testing%20is%207.1%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usgs.gov%2Fprograms%2Fearthquake-hazards%2Fmodified-mercalli-intensity-scale%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMMI%20scale%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20larger%20numbers%20meaning%20stronger%20vibrations.%20The%20EOS%20Classic%20Organic%20registered%206.4%2C%20significantly%20lower%20than%20most%20beds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20while%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20I%20had%20my%20wife%20join%20me%20and%20move%20around%20a%20bit%20to%20simulate%20tossing%20and%20turning.%20I%20could%20just%20barely%20feel%20her%20while%20she%20did%20this.%20Though%20I'm%20a%20light%20sleeper%2C%20it's%20doubtful%20the%20slight%20jostling%20would%20wake%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impressive%20combination%20of%20edge%20support%20and%20motion%20isolation%20makes%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20an%20outstanding%20choice%20for%20couples.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220454e0a6-ea65-4a36-8fe8-0aaaf1b341e5%5C%22%3ETrial%20period%20and%20warranty%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENaturepedic%20offers%20a%20100-night%20sleep%20trial%20with%20the%20EOS%20Classic.%20If%20you%20decide%20it%20isn't%20right%20for%20you%20after%2030%20nights%2C%20you%20can%20return%20it%20for%20a%20full%20refund.%20During%20the%20trial%20period%2C%20Naturepedic%20lets%20you%20swap%20out%20the%20latex%20comfort%20layer%20for%20a%20different%20firmness%20for%20free.%20If%20you%20return%20your%20mattress%2C%20Naturepedic%20will%20donate%20it%20to%20charity%20or%20recycle%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturepedic%20backs%20the%20EOS%20Classic%20Organic%20with%20a%2025-year%20warranty.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20some%20catches.%20You%20need%20to%20use%20a%20supportive%20foundation%20with%20the%20mattress.%20If%20it's%20a%20slatted%20base%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20slats%20or%20supports%20must%20not%20be%20more%20than%203%20inches%20apart.%20Also%2C%20the%20warranty%20is%20void%20if%20the%20law%20label%20is%20missing%20or%20damage%20is%20caused%20by%20jumping%20on%20the%20bed.%20Flaws%20in%20workmanship%20or%20defects%2C%20including%20the%20mattress%20indenting%20more%20than%201.5%20inches%2C%20will%20be%20fixed%20or%20replaced%20at%20Naturepedic's%20discretion%20during%20the%20first%2010%20years%20of%20the%20warranty.%20After%20that%2C%20component%20repair%20or%20replacement%20will%20be%20prorated.%20Shipping%20costs%20for%20the%20bed%20and%20any%20replacement%20are%20not%20covered%20by%20the%20warranty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229efad279-39c2-4e99-afee-59d67ee5130d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20negative%20of%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20is%20its%20heat%20retention.%20I%20don't%20like%20waking%20up%20sweaty%20and%20wet%20at%20night%2C%20but%20that%20happened%20on%20the%20EOS%20Classic.%20Hot%20sleepers%20might%20want%20to%20consider%20alternatives%2C%20though%20cold%20sleepers%20may%20welcome%20the%20cozy%20warmth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20setup%20process%20was%20a%20pain%20in%20the%20butt.%20It%20took%20about%20four%20times%20as%20long%20as%20other%20mattresses.%20In%20a%20perfect%20world%2C%20Naturepedic%20would%20send%20you%20the%20EOS%20Classic%20Organic%20already%20assembled%20with%20your%20preferred%20comfort%20layers%20installed%20the%20way%20you%20want%20them.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20benefits%20to%20how%20they%20do%20it%20now%2C%20and%20if%20assembling%20the%20bed%20yourself%20is%20too%20off-putting%2C%20you%20can%20always%20spring%20for%20white-glove%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20at%20%243%2C499%20for%20a%20queen%2C%20the%20Naturepedic%20EOS%20Classic%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20organic%20mattresses%20I've%20tested.%20However%2C%20when%20you%20think%20about%20the%2025-year%20warranty%2C%20it%20kind%20of%20puts%20the%20purchase%20in%20perspective.%20The%20is%20a%20bed%20made%20of%20high-quality%20organic%20materials%20that%20are%20meant%20to%20last.%20And%2C%20if%20your%20comfort%20preferences%20change%20over%20time%2C%20you%20can%20adjust%20the%20firmness%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.naturepedic.com%2Fnewlayers-selectsize%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuying%20new%20coils%20or%20a%20new%20latex%20comfort%20layer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2293b7df4a-d706-488a-8244-6f764a6f7073%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Alternatives%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222460%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20man%20lying%20on%20the