al%20illustrates%20how%20farmers%20can%20capitalise%20on%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20say%20farmers%20are%20currently%20buying%20electricity%20at%20Rs%208%20or%209%20per%20unit.%20Once%20they%20install%20agrivoltaics%2C%20electricity%20will%20be%20sold%20to%20them%20for%20Rs%205%2C%20which%20is%20cheaper.%20This%20way%2C%20they%20are%20minimising%20their%20expenditure%20and%20reducing%20their%20dependency%20on%20the%20grid.%E2%80%9D%20For%20farmers%20who%20are%20still%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20model%20going%20against%20the%20grain%2C%20Vimal%20has%20another%20solution.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fvideo.php%3Fheight%3D314%26href%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Faskagrivijay%252Fvideos%252F404259222478618%252F%26show_text%3Dfalse%26width%3D560%26t%3D0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22314%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgriVijay%20has%20launched%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20%E2%80%98Vertical%20Bifacial%20Solar%20AgriVoltaics%20Project%E2%80%99%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Next2Sun%20and%20Wattkraft%2C%20in%20Maharashtra.%20%E2%80%9COur%20innovative%20Agri-PV%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20simultaneously%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F420549%2Fbhaskar-solar-lantern-in-indian-villages-green-energy-projects-in-rural-indian-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20solar%20energy%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20agriculture%2C%20maintaining%20over%2090%20percent%20land%20usability%20for%20farming.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20approach%20not%20only%20optimises%20land%20use%20but%20also%20ensures%20soil%20preservation%2C%20garnering%20substantial%20public%20support.%20By%20seamlessly%20integrating%20energy%20generation%20with%20agricultural%20operations%2C%20the%20Next2Sun%20solution%20exemplifies%20efficient%20and%20sustainable%20land%20management.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%3Cem%3E%20Agrivoltaics%20in%20India%3A%20Fertile%20Ground%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20the%20Institute%20for%20Energy%20Economics%20and%20Financial%20Analysis%20(IEEFA)%2C%20authored%20by%20Dr%20Charles%20Worringham%20%E2%80%94%20a%20notable%20name%20in%20the%20space%20of%20green%20energy%20who%20has%20been%20closely%20tracking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F55755%2Felectrifying-india-project-belaku%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20energy%20transition%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20supports%20the%20vertical%20setup%20idea.%20When%20mounted%20vertically%2C%20like%20fences%20facing%20east%20and%20west%2C%20they%20produce%20peak%20power%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20afternoon%2C%20unlike%20horizontal%20panels%20that%20peak%20at%20midday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20configuration%20can%20help%20the%20grid%20by%20producing%20power%20closer%20to%20peak%20demand%20time%2C%20which%20is%20typically%20in%20the%20evening.%20This%20might%20allow%20certain%20loads%20like%20residential%20cooling%20to%20be%20brought%20forward%20a%20little%20and%20use%20that%20power%20directly%2C%20or%20by%20shortening%20the%20time%20between%20generation%20and%20use%2C%20make%20battery%20storage%20easier%20and%20more%20flexible%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Worringham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20bending%20the%20formula%2C%20the%20vertical%20set-up%20will%20solve%20all%20of%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20anxieties%20about%20the%20land%20being%20occupied%2C%20Vimal%20is%20sure.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fagrivoltaics-9-1745327046.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20a%20climate-controlled%20approach%2C%20the%20m